new <- x %>%
  left_join(y, by = "president")

xent <- new %>%
  unnest_tokens(word, text) %>%
  inner_join(get_sentiments("nrc"))
## Joining, by = "word"
xent %>%
  group_by(party) %>%
  count(sentiment)
